=== Per-permutation invariant under GS flip ===
  n=4, bits=0: fwd(P,T)+fwd(P,T_flip) values = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
  n=4, bits=7: fwd(P,T)+fwd(P,T_flip) values = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
  n=4, bits=7: fwd(P,T)+fwd(P,T_flip) values = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
  n=5, bits=0: fwd(P,T)+fwd(P,T_flip) values = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8]
  n=5, bits=7: fwd(P,T)+fwd(P,T_flip) values = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8]
  n=5, bits=63: fwd(P,T)+fwd(P,T_flip) values = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8]


=== Consequence for H ===
Distribution of c(P) = 2*bb_fwd(P) + nbb_steps(P):

  n=4: c(P) distribution: {0: 1, 1: 3, 2: 5, 3: 6, 4: 5, 5: 3, 6: 1}
    bb_fwd range: [0, 3]
    nbb_steps range: [0, 3]
    c(P) is NOT constant

  n=5: c(P) distribution: {0: 1, 1: 4, 2: 14, 3: 24, 4: 34, 5: 24, 6: 14, 7: 4, 8: 1}
    bb_fwd range: [0, 4]
    nbb_steps range: [0, 4]
    c(P) is NOT constant

  n=6: c(P) distribution: {0: 1, 1: 5, 2: 26, 3: 76, 4: 149, 5: 206, 6: 149, 7: 76, 8: 26, 9: 5, 10: 1}
    bb_fwd range: [0, 5]
    nbb_steps range: [0, 5]
    c(P) is NOT constant
